high_descs: Turn around completely, walk almost to the wall, then turn right to face the desk.
Pick up the alarm clock that is closest to the front of the desk.
Turn to the left, walk to the wall, turn to the left again and walk up to the nightstand.
Place the alarm clock down on the nightstand between the two CDs.
anns.task_desc: Move an alarm clock to the nightstand.

high_descs: Turn around and walk to the desk on the right.
